<p>Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian,</p>

<p>More importantly, we need to know the style and color of a scale (major, minor, dom7, bright, dark, etc.)</p>

<p>From brightest to darkest (notice that we are slowly dropping the pitch of notes, in the same order as we would along the circl of 5ths)</p>

