<h3 id="dominant-7-harmony-scales">Dominant 7 Harmony Scales</h3>

<p>Lydian Flat 7
Altered Scale - flat 9, sharp 9, natural 3, sharp 11, flat 13, flat 7
Normally does not include the 5th, but the 5th is still usable in this scale.</p>

<p>Symmetric Diminished - sounds like the diminished chord
b9, sharp 9, natural 3, sharp 11, natural 5, natural 6, flat 7</p>

